parameters:
When we first came here, I didn't notice at all. This
doll...

It must be what the village chief was talking about. There's
a protrusion on the back.
Alright, let's try pushing it! Click!
--Incredible! A secret passage to the back has appeared!?

What an amazing mechanism. If they took this much
precaution...
I'm hoping the ship inside is something substantial.
What the heck!? This isn't a boat, it's more like a tub!

...Can four people really ride in this? It's obviously
impossible.

You're kidding me, Kokuyou Tengu!? What's the meaning of
this!?

Whoa, calm down, Karin--! Don't take it out on me! It was
the exile leader who said there would definitely be a
boat...!

...It's a boat alright, but without sails, this tiny thing
can't navigate the rough open sea. It'd be swallowed by the
waves and sunk in no time.

...! (What should we do? Is there no choice but to turn back
now?)
----!? You, what are you doing here!?

Oh my, my! What do we have here? Criminals trying to escape
the island by boat?
This is serious! We need to call the officials!

You're under arrest, you're under arrest! Let's hear your
explanation!
~~~~!! The exile leaders!? And officials too!?
...! Could it be that we've been trapped...?

This island is short on food... By spreading information
about a boat and catching the foolish criminals who bite,
they're sentenced to death for attempting to escape the
island--Hehehe, it's a rational system for reducing mouths
to feed, right?

All four of you are under arrest for attempting to escape
the island! Don't resist!
Get captured by the officials without resistance

If we're going to be caught anyway, we might as well board
this boat and head to sea--!

No good, Miss Karin! With such a small boat, if we set sail
we'll just become seaweed fodder immediately! Stay calm!
大人しく役人に捕縛される

(There are so many officials at the entrance... I could
break through and escape on my own, but I can't just leave
everyone behind...)

Pfft... To think we were danced around by false
information... We've really screwed up big time...
Don't run! Stop resisting, you vile criminals!
Ahhhh...! Nooo! Let go of me!

No use... Can't leave Kachou-san behind and escape... As
much as it pains me, we should surrender quietly, Miss
Karin...

Hahaha! That's a good look for you, Karin! This is what you
get for making fools out of us! Show me more of that
frustration!

You bastard! To think you were in cahoots with the
officials...! How dare you trap and deceive me like this!

Heheh. Just sending an old man with not much time left on
his way. And I'm grateful that you even took care of the
disobedient Karin for us, baldy♪ Haha!
Capture all of them! Don't make any futile resistance!

--Karin and the other three were captured by the officials
of Mujou Island...
